sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Frontend as Frontend React
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Flouci as Flouci API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Client->>Frontend: Valide le panier (checkout)
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/orders
    Note right of Frontend: {items[], deliveryAddress, deliveryDate, paymentMethod}
    Gateway->>Order: Proxy requête (JWT vérifié)
    Order->>Order: Calcule sous-total, TVA 19%, frais livraison
    Order->>DB: INSERT order + order_items
    DB-->>Order: Commande créée (status: PENDING)
    Order->>DB: INSERT invoice
    Order-->>Gateway: {order, invoice}
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 201 Created

    alt paymentMethod == FLOUCI
        Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/payments/flouci/initiate
        Gateway->>Order: {orderId}
        Order->>DB: INSERT payment (method: FLOUCI, status: PENDING)
        Order->>Flouci: POST /generate_payment (montant en millimes)
        Flouci-->>Order: {paymentUrl, payment_id}
        Order-->>Frontend: {paymentUrl}
        Frontend->>Client: Redirection vers Flouci
        Client->>Flouci: Effectue le paiement en ligne
        Flouci-->>Frontend: Retour (success_link)
        Frontend->>Gateway: GET /api/payments/flouci/verify/:id
        Gateway->>Order: Vérification
        Order->>Flouci: GET /verify_payment/:id
        Flouci-->>Order: {status: SUCCESS}
        Order->>DB: UPDATE payment status = COMPLETED
        Order->>DB: UPDATE order status = CONFIRMED
        Order-->>Frontend: {verified: true}
    else paymentMethod == CASH
        Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/payments/create
        Gateway->>Order: {orderId}
        Order->>DB: INSERT payment (method: CASH, status: PENDING)
        Order-->>Frontend: Paiement en attente à la livraison
    end

    Frontend-->>Client: Confirmation de commande
